{"markdown":{"yaml":{"format":"html","page-layout":"full"},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n```{=html}\n\n<!-- HERO CARD Landing banner-->\n\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css\">\n\n<div class=\"hero-split\">\n  <div class=\"hero-left\">\n    <img src=\"images/summer_school_logo.svg\" alt=\"Summer School Logo\" class=\"hero-logo\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"hero-right\">\n    <h1>The Art and Science of Uncertainty and the Future</h1>\n    <p class=\"subtitle\">An Interdisciplinary Summer School focused on understanding, modeling, and navigating uncertainty to build resilient futures.</p>\n    \n    <div class=\"hero-details-grid\">\n        <div class=\"hero-detail-item\">\n            <i class=\"fas fa-calendar-alt\"></i> 22-27 June 2026 \n        </div>\n        <div class=\"hero-detail-separator\"> | </div>\n        <div class=\"hero-detail-item\">\n            <i class=\"fas fa-map-marker-alt\"></i> Cardiff, Wales, UK\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"hero-detail-separator\"> | </div>\n        <div class=\"hero-detail-item\">\n            <a href=\"mailto:halgamuwehewagehr@cardiff.ac.uk\" style=\"color: inherit; text-decoration: none;\"> <!-- ADD YOUR EMAIL --><i class=\"fas fa-envelope\"></i> Contact Us\n            </a>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <a href=\"https://forms.gle/VChKXLDcmK4aAKmQA\" class=\"btn-custom btn-primary\"> <!-- ADD YOUR APPLICATION LINK --><i class=\"fas fa-external-link-alt\"></i> Apply Now - Deadline: 1 March 2026\n    </a>\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n\n\n```{=html}\n<!-- About page-->\n\n<div class=\"page-container\">\n\n    <!-- Section Header from image -->\n    <div class=\"section-header\">\n        <h1>Engage with Uncertainty. Shape the Future.</h1>\n        <p>This summer school provides a unique opportunity to build capacity, foster collaboration, and advance research into our uncertain futures.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Grid for the four info cards -->\n    <div class=\"grid-container\">\n\n        <!-- Card 1 -->\n        <div class=\"info-card\">\n            <h3>Build Futures Capacity</h3>\n            <p>Master futures-oriented tools from probabilistic modelling and foresight to speculative design and storytelling.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- Card 2 -->\n        <div class=\"info-card\">\n            <h3>Foster Collaboration</h3>\n            <p>Join a select, interdisciplinary cohort of 40 participants to build vibrant new networks across Wales and internationally.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- Card 3 -->\n        <div class=\"info-card\">\n            <h3>Advance Applied Research</h3>\n            <p>Work in teams on live challenges, exploring domains such as climate change, AI governance, and health resilience.</p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <!-- Card 4 -->\n        <div class=\"info-card\">\n            <h3>Pilot Creative Methods</h3>\n            <p>Experiment with creative practices and participatory approaches like 'future-jams' and 'signal sharing' to engage with uncertainty.</p>\n        </div>\n\n    </div> <!-- End grid-container -->\n\n</div>\n\n```\n\n\n```{=html}\n<!-- MAIN CONTENT AREA -->\n<div class=\"page-container\">\n\n    <!-- NEW KEY DATES SECTION -->\n    <div class=\"content-card\">\n        <h2>Important Dates</h2>\n        <table class=\"key-dates-table\"> <!-- Changed to table -->\n            <tbody>\n                <tr>\n                    <td class=\"date\">15 November 2025</td>\n                    <td class=\"event\">Application open</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td class=\"date\">01 March 2026</td>\n                    <td class=\"event\">Application close</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td class=\"date\">01 April 2026</td>\n                    <td class=\"event\">Programme published</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td class=\"date\">05 July 2026</td>\n                    <td class=\"event\">Welcome reception drink</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td class=\"date\">06–11 July 2026</td>\n                    <td class=\"event\">Summer school</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td class=\"date\">12 July 2026</td>\n                    <td class=\"event\">Site visit</td>\n                </tr>\n            </tbody>\n        </table> <!-- End of table -->\n    </div>\n    \n</div>\n```\n\n\n{{< include about/index.qmd >}}\n\n\n{{< include program/index.qmd >}}\n\n\n{{< include speakers/index.qmd >}}\n\n\n{{< include org_and_sponsors/index.qmd >}}\n\n\n{{< include footer/index.qmd >}}\n\n\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n```{=html}\n\n<!-- HERO CARD Landing banner-->\n\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css\">\n\n<div class=\"hero-split\">\n  <div class=\"hero-left\">\n    <img src=\"images/summer_school_logo.svg\" alt=\"Summer School Logo\" class=\"hero-logo\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"hero-right\">\n    <h1>The Art and Science of Uncertainty and the Future</h1>\n    <p class=\"subtitle\">An Interdisciplinary Summer School focused on understanding, modeling, and navigating uncertainty to build resilient futures.</p>\n    \n    <div class=\"hero-details-grid\">\n        <div class=\"hero-detail-item\">\n            <i class=\"fas fa-calendar-alt\"></i> 22-27 June 2026 \n        </div>\n        <div class=\"hero-detail-separator\"> | </div>\n        <div class=\"hero-detail-item\">\n            <i class=\"fas fa-map-marker-alt\"></i> Cardiff, Wales, UK\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"hero-detail-separator\"> | </div>\n        <div class=\"hero-detail-item\">\n            <a href=\"mailto:halgamuwehewagehr@cardiff.ac.uk\" style=\"color: inherit; text-decoration: none;\"> <!-- ADD YOUR EMAIL --><i class=\"fas fa-envelope\"></i> Contact Us\n            </a>\